code: public final ConfigurableBeanFactory getBeanFactory() {     return this.beanFactory. }
@Nullable public final Scope getScope() {     return this.scope. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object other) {     if (this == other) {         return true.     }     if (!(other instanceof BeanExpressionContext)) {         return false.     }     BeanExpressionContext otherContext = (BeanExpressionContext) other.     return (this.beanFactory == otherContext.beanFactory && this.scope == otherContext.scope). }
